}}</ref>

用于树莓派1、2、3的[[openSUSE|openSUSE]]使用IceWM为默认轻量用户界面。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://en.opensuse.org/HCL:Raspberry_Pi3 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-12-27 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108105752/https://en.opensuse.org/HCL:Raspberry_Pi3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>用于树莓派3的[[SUSE_Linux_Enterprise_Server|SUSE Linux Enterprise Server]]同样使用IceWM。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.marksei.com/suse-linux-enterprise-server-gains-raspberry-pi-3-support/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-12-27 |archive-date=2020-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921134603/https://www.marksei.com/suse-linux-enterprise-server-gains-raspberry-pi-3-support/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

